Expr.ExprTextDesc: IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D_Solicitor"."TOTAL_PAY_AMT", 0) + IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D_Solicitor"."TOTAL_GIFTAID_AMT", 0) - IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D_Solicitor"."TOTAL_PAY_AMT_SP", 0) - IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D_Solicitor"."TOTAL_GIFTAID_AMT_SP", 0) + IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D_Solicitor"."TOTAL_ORDER_GROSS_AMT_SP", 0)

LogicalColumn.Description: This is the banding into which the Gross Stewardship value falls e.g. 10-49k

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party Solicitor"."Stewardship Value" < 10000 THEN '£0-£9k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party Solicitor"."Stewardship Value" < 50000 THEN '£10k-£49k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party Solicitor"."Stewardship Value" < 100000 THEN '£50k-£99k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party Solicitor"."Stewardship Value" < 500000 THEN '£100k-£499k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party Solicitor"."Stewardship Value" < 1000000 THEN '£500k-£999k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party Solicitor"."Stewardship Value" >= 1000000 THEN '£1m+' ELSE '' END
